    "en": {
      "title": "25 protesters were arrested",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "Police Media Spokesperson Nihal Taltuwa said that 25 people who participated in the demonstration rally organized by All University Students' Union in Colombo today (30) have been arrested.",
        "Demonstrations were held demanding that the repressions should stop and all the detained university student union organizer Vasantha Mudalike and others should be released.",
        "It is mentioned that the police used water cannon and tear gas to disperse the protest rally which started at the hospital."
      ],
